message: Hi Bob, I hope you're well. I have an exceptional product available that I believe will perfectly suit your needs. Based on its quality and unique features, I'm offering it for $25000. Please let me know if this meets your expectations or if you have any questions.

Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the quality and unique features of the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of a lower price point. I'd like to make a counteroffer of $6000. I believe this is a fair price considering my budget and the value I see in the product.
